Nibbles game.

Implement the following game modes:

  for at least two players on one computer,
  for at least two more players on PC (network game)
  to play against the computer (scalable artificial intelligence).

The game must fulfill the following functions:

  keeping rules,
  loading game levels (maps) of the file (create a suitable format)
  announcing the end of the game and its outcome


Worms is a game where each player controls a worm. He moves across the screen, leaving a trail, which increases gradually consuming food. While trying to nenabourat obstacles (walls, other worms). Rules can be added additional gameplay elements.

